OL,7,FSynod members will debate and vote on
OL,8,Fa new safeguarding model for the
OL,9,FChurch of England on Tuesday.
OL,11,FTwo so-called models for independent
OL,12,Fsafeguarding will be presented to
OL,13,FSynod, following reviews in recent
OL,14,Fyears by former chairwoman of the
OL,15,Fnational Independent Inquiry into
OL,16,FChild Sexual Abuse (IICSA) Professor
OL,17,FAlexis Jay, and barrister Sarah
OL,18,FWilkinson.
