OL,7,FThe Synod is sitting for its first
OL,8,Fsession since the resignation of the
OL,9,Farchbishop of Canterbury Justin Welby,
OL,10,Fafter safeguarding failures.
OL,12,FHe quit after pressure following a
OL,13,Freview which found Christian camp
OL,14,Fleader and prolific serial abuser John
OL,15,FSmyth might have been brought to
OL,16,Fjustice had Mr Welby formally reported
OL,17,Fhim to police five years before the
OL,18,Fbarrister's death.
