OL,4,Cnew safeguarding model for Church of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FIn standing down, Mr Welby also noted
OL,8,Fhis "long felt and profound sense of
OL,9,Fshame at the historic safeguarding
OL,10,Ffailures of the Church of England".
OL,12,FThe safeguarding debate in the Church
OL,13,Fhas been a long-running one, and calls
OL,14,Fhave also been made in recent months
OL,15,Ffor Mr Welby's temporary stand-in,
OL,16,FArchbishop of York Stephen Cottrell,
OL,17,Fto stand down.
