OL,7,FMr Cottrell has refused to quit after
OL,8,Fdisclosures that a priest at the
OL,9,Fcentre of a sexual abuse case was
OL,10,Ftwice re-appointed under him while he
OL,11,Fwas serving as Bishop of Chelmsford.
OL,13,FHe has acknowledged things "could have
OL,14,Fbeen handled differently" but,
OL,15,Fappearing to reject calls to resign,
OL,16,Fhas pledged to "do what I can" to
OL,17,Fbring about independent scrutiny of
OL,18,Fsafeguarding in the Church.
