OL,7,FHe has also said it was "not possible"
OL,8,Fto remove the priest in that case from
OL,9,Foffice until fresh complaints were
OL,10,Fmade in 2019.
OL,12,FOne model, known as model four, would
OL,13,Fsee all safeguarding officers
OL,14,Fcurrently working in dioceses,
OL,15,Fcathedrals and the national Church
OL,16,Ftransferred to work for a new
OL,17,Findependent organisation.
