OL,7,FMr Cottrell admitted on Monday he has
OL,8,F"made mistakes" but said he is
OL,9,Fdetermined to "lead the change we all
OL,10,Fknow we need" in the Church of
OL,11,FEngland, which has been plagued by
OL,12,Fabuse safeguarding failures.
OL,14,FHe also survived a vote to stop him
OL,15,Fgiving a presidential address as the
OL,16,FGeneral Synod began on Monday.
