OL,7,FSeparately, Mr Cottrell has also
OL,8,F"categorically rejected" allegations
OL,9,Fthat he bullied members of a committee
OL,10,Fto secure John Perumbalath's
OL,11,Fappointment as Bishop of Liverpool.
OL,13,FMr Perumbalath resigned as bishop last
OL,14,Fmonth following media coverage of
OL,15,Fsexual assault and harassment
OL,16,Fallegations against him, which he
OL,17,Fdenies.
